Package waitersProgram.model

Class OrderManager

java.lang.Object
waitersProgram.model.OrderManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
OrderManegerInterface
public class OrderManager extends Object implements OrderManegerInterface
The OrderManager class. This class is created in order to efficiently manage every order processed by the restaurant system. Each order is stored in a specific ArrayList (a stack) according to its status. The class provides some methods that move orders from a stack to another and change their status.
